# Normalize line endings across platforms.
#
# Without this, Git's core.autocrlf on Windows rewrites LF -> CRLF on checkout,
# which makes Prettier (configured with the default endOfLine: "lf") flag every
# file in the repo. Forcing LF for text keeps local `format:check` in sync with
# CI (which runs on Linux) regardless of the contributor's OS.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary files: never apply line-ending conversion.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.svg text eol=lf
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
